main event: A white object appeared in the sky over Semarang, Indonesia on February 3, 1955.
interesting points: The object appeared to be about the size of a star but larger.
The object was seen moving, suddenly stopping, and then moving again.
Almost all Semarang residents witnessed the object.
The report is from the ATIC (Air Technical Intelligence Center) Document 105752.
sighted object: a white object in the sky
